                    <msContents>
                        <summary/>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <title>Magical prayers</title>
                            <note>The text is arranged in twelve rectangles written alternately in red and black ink.</note>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                                <title ref="LIT4570MagicPr" type="incomplete"/>
                                <note>Text written in red.</note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስሙ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ መፍትሔ፡ ሥራይ፡ ዘተቀድሐት፡ እም፹ወ፩መጻሕፍት፡ ዘረክበት፡
                                    በኢየሩሳሌም፡ ጁር፡ አቅጁር፡ መቅጁር፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> 
                                    በበረከተ፡ ንጉሥነ፡ <persName ref="PRS9142TaklaGi">ተክለ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡</persName> 
                                    ወበጳጳስነ፡ <persName ref="PRS11137QerellosII">ቄርሎስ፡</persName> ዘኮነ፡ ሥራይ፡ ይትፈታሕ፡</incipit>
                                <note>The end is missing.</note>
                                <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                                <title ref="LIT2243salotb" type="incomplete"/>
                                <note>Text written in black and arranged for the days of the week starting with Sunday and ending in the middle of the 
                                    prayer for Tuesday.</note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ባርያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ ዛር፡ ወነገርጋር፡ ወጋኔነ፡ ቀትር፡ ወእምኵሉ፡ እኩይ፡ 
                                    ግብር፡ ንጽሕፍ፡ እንከ፡ ነገረ፡ መሥጥም፡ ጸሎት፡ ዘዕለተ፡ እሁድ፡ ዓባይ፡ ዘባርያ፡ ወሌጌዎን፡ በአህያ፡ በሻራህያ፡</incipit>
                                <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            </msItem>
                        </msItem> 
